Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那樣在太陽下走下去的話一定挺不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相幫助祭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大地人們請客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是感謝我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放醬汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要放蛋黃醬
